name: MovieRatingof
0: ”Alexa, tell movie rating of Iron Man”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie rating of
des: We all want know the rating of the movie we are going to watch. I have integrated this in an Alexa skill, it gives rating of the movie or any TV series as it is on IMDB and Rotten Tomatoes. It uses the OMDb api and Lambda function.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
